education.description: The main campus of the University of Limpopo is located in Turfloop, near Polokwane (formerly Pietersburg), the capital city of Limpopo province. The university provides modern facilities for teaching, learning, research, and recreational activities.

experience.Title: Lab Assistant
experience.Description: A Lab Assistant is essential to the smooth operation of a laboratory, providing critical support to scientists and researchers. Through diligent maintenance of equipment, precise preparation and execution of experiments, and meticulous data management, Lab Assistants help advance scientific research and innovation. Their role demands a combination of technical skills, attention to detail, and a commitment to maintaining a safe and organized laboratory environment.
